{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#6221: v-bind没有响应式",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:26:02.895798+00:00",
  "text": "v-bind没有响应式\n\n### Vue version\n\nvue3\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://sfc.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n<template>\r\n    <button @click=\"test\">增加宽度</button>\r\n    <div :style=\"config.style\">\r\n        <h1>1</h1>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <br/>\r\n    <div v-bind=\"config\">\r\n        <h1>2</h1>\r\n    </div>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<script setup>\r\n    import { reactive } from 'vue';\r\n\r\n    let width = 100;\r\n    let config = reactive({\r\n        style: {\r\n            width: `${width}px`,\r\n            height: '100px',\r\n            background: 'orange',\r\n        },\r\n    });\r\n    let test = () => {\r\n        width += 50;\r\n        config.style.width = `${width}px`;\r\n    };\r\n</script>\r\n\n\n### What is expected?\n\n有响应式\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\n无响应式\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "has workaround",
    "🔩 p2-edge-case"
  ],
